&lt;/audio>
&lt;p>अच्युतं केशवं रामनारायणं कृष्णदामोदरं वासुदेवं हरिम्। &lt;br>
श्रीधरं माधवं गोपिकावल्लभं जानकीनायकं रामचंद्रं भजे॥1॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Bhava Sagara Tarana Karana He - भवसागर तारण कारण हे</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/bhava-sagara-tarana-karana-he/</link><pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/samskrutyatra/bhava-sagara-tarana-karana-he/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/samskrutyatra/Sri-Ramakrishna.jpg" alt="" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">भवसागर तारण कारण हे
&lt;div id="%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%B0-%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3-%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A3-%E0%A4%B9" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
